{% extends "layouts/base.njk" %}

{% block content %}
  <section class="legal-section">
    <div class="container legal-shell">
      <p class="eyebrow">Privacy</p>
      <h1>Privacy Notice</h1>
      <p>This website is a placeholder concept for {{ site.businessName }}. The public frontend is generated statically from structured content files, and the default setup does not include public accounts, comments, or live newsletter signup forms.</p>
      <p>If someone emails or calls the published contact details, any personal information should be used only to respond to editorial, pastoral, collaboration, or administrative enquiries and retained only as long as reasonably necessary.</p>
      <p>Before any real launch, replace this placeholder notice with a project-specific privacy policy that reflects the actual organisation, mailing tools, analytics setup, donation flow, and safeguarding responsibilities.</p>
      <p>For privacy queries, use the published contact email: <a href="mailto:{{ site.contact.email }}">{{ site.contact.email }}</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
{% endblock %}
